Task # 01

Try to achive the Following(Replace the PlaceHolders with your Designated Name)

1) Create a data base [Database_Name]

2) Create a User of your choice with the Encrypted Password

3) Grant all permissions TO user.


Solution # 01 

--Created a Test Database 
Create Database [Database_Name];

--Created a Test_User
Create user [User_Name] Encrypted password ['PWD'];

--Granted permissions for the Test_User
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON SCHEMA PUBLIC TO [User_Name];
